JOHANNESBURG - Singing for your supper is not a new concept and some South African artists have time again done just that. While there has been criticism by some on social media in the past, there are stars that have aligned themselves with the ruling party with some seemingly making a living by performing at their gatherings. eNCA compiled a list of artists that will happily sing the ANC’s praises with the upcoming elective conference starting on Saturday. Mafikizolo Riky Rick Cici AKA Kelly Khumalo Chomee Teboho Casper Nyovest And after all the politicking, politicians too need to jiggy sometimes... WATCH: President Zuma hits the 'dab' eNCA